WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.400 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:05.400 --> 00:00:07.440 align:middle line:84%
In this video, we'll
see how to upload videos

00:00:07.440 --> 00:00:10.310 align:middle line:90%
using Brightcove Campaign.

00:00:10.310 --> 00:00:12.260 align:middle line:84%
Brightcove Campaign
provides an easy to use

00:00:12.260 --> 00:00:15.350 align:middle line:84%
interface for adding
videos to your account.

00:00:15.350 --> 00:00:18.320 align:middle line:84%
To upload videos,
go to the videos tab

00:00:18.320 --> 00:00:21.180 align:middle line:90%
and click the upload button.

00:00:21.180 --> 00:00:22.850 align:middle line:84%
The file browser
will open, allowing

00:00:22.850 --> 00:00:25.190 align:middle line:84%
you to browse and select one
or more files for upload.

00:00:25.190 --> 00:00:28.510 align:middle line:90%


00:00:28.510 --> 00:00:31.240 align:middle line:84%
After selecting files,
the upload will begin.

00:00:31.240 --> 00:00:33.920 align:middle line:90%


00:00:33.920 --> 00:00:36.460 align:middle line:84%
You can also drag and drop
files from your file system

00:00:36.460 --> 00:00:39.330 align:middle line:90%
to the upload panel.

00:00:39.330 --> 00:00:42.015 align:middle line:84%
When you drop the files,
the upload will begin.

00:00:42.015 --> 00:00:44.600 align:middle line:90%


00:00:44.600 --> 00:00:47.210 align:middle line:84%
Brightcove recommends
assigning a video content type

00:00:47.210 --> 00:00:49.250 align:middle line:90%
to each video.

00:00:49.250 --> 00:00:51.950 align:middle line:84%
When videos are assigned
a video content type,

00:00:51.950 --> 00:00:54.110 align:middle line:84%
Brightcove can
compile your analytics

00:00:54.110 --> 00:00:56.450 align:middle line:84%
with those of similar
videos, and provide

00:00:56.450 --> 00:00:59.180 align:middle line:84%
more robust analytics
that includes Brightcove's

00:00:59.180 --> 00:01:02.130 align:middle line:90%
video benchmark score.

00:01:02.130 --> 00:01:05.930 align:middle line:84%
You can close the upload
panel by clicking on the X.

00:01:05.930 --> 00:01:09.220 align:middle line:84%
And reopen it by
clicking upload.

00:01:09.220 --> 00:01:11.170 align:middle line:84%
You should remain
on the videos tab

00:01:11.170 --> 00:01:13.780 align:middle line:84%
until all files have
a status of uploaded.

00:01:13.780 --> 00:01:16.583 align:middle line:90%


00:01:16.583 --> 00:01:18.250 align:middle line:84%
All of the videos in
the account will be

00:01:18.250 --> 00:01:21.240 align:middle line:90%
listed in the body of the page.

00:01:21.240 --> 00:01:23.300 align:middle line:84%
Note that for newly
uploaded videos,

00:01:23.300 --> 00:01:26.210 align:middle line:84%
it may take a few minutes for
the processing to complete,

00:01:26.210 --> 00:01:29.560 align:middle line:84%
and for the thumbnail
images to appear.

00:01:29.560 --> 00:01:33.660 align:middle line:84%
You can edit video properties
by clicking on the video name.

00:01:33.660 --> 00:01:37.640 align:middle line:84%
Editing video properties is
covered in another video.

00:01:37.640 --> 00:01:40.000 align:middle line:90%